text: Lucy Miszewski (born 16 February 2000) is a South African water-polo player. She competed for the South Africa women's national water polo team in the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * lucy- miszewski- * lucy-miszewski * water-polo-database Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:South African water polo players
